    "name": "Ground Water - Episode of Dhanra",
    "steam_appid": 3136460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款手工打造的短篇叙事平台游戏，关于挤压与追寻自由的旅程。跟随罗西穿越檀拉村的冲突，踏上寻找治愈家园诅咒的冒险。穿越曲折的道路和触感鲜明的环境，展现罗西强大的挤压能力与多样容器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是 <i>Ground Water</i> 传奇的第一章：一个独立的故事，引领你进入这个世界和它的谜团，同时为未来的发展奠定舞台。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Piraiya和挤压</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ground-Water设定在一个由名为Piraiya的智能生物居住的世界。它们的身体结构奇特而简单，基本上是充满水的容器。它们主要通过滑动来移动，通过挤压身体来产生和释放内部水的张力，以执行所有动作。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/82a2f1ff79b61c892cb7bb507705f134.poster.avif?t=1771652205\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/82a2f1ff79b61c892cb7bb507705f134.webm?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/82a2f1ff79b61c892cb7bb507705f134.mp4?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roshi和他的容器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追求自由的主角Roshi是一个年轻的Piraiya，他正在发现改变容器的形状可以导致与周围世界的多样行为和互动。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/0214774a73d9aec49e739d20677cf63f.avif?t=1771652205\" width=232 height=496 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高塔 - 着陆时轻巧，但头部碰撞强烈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/b5472131f9772fa85aab63ac11d96443.avif?t=1771652205\" width=342 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >方形 - 像冠军一样着陆并跳起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/768a2eb418f6202eb60a6ddb9d32f989.avif?t=1771652205\" width=424 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宽型 - 压倒性地着陆。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >触觉环境</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roshi的多才多艺与玩家可以以多种方式互动的同样适应性强的触觉环境元素相匹配。这些元素融入到精心设计的区域中，路径分支、交汇、交错，让玩家能够创造自己独特的游戏故事和时刻。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/3ab404e0b367f58f942070ab53872105.poster.avif?t=1771652205\" width=730 height=570 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/3ab404e0b367f58f942070ab53872105.webm?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/3ab404e0b367f58f942070ab53872105.mp4?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/7773dca21431a6e1726e7f4d8d8c9443.poster.avif?t=1771652205\" width=780 height=1068 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/7773dca21431a6e1726e7f4d8d8c9443.webm?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/7773dca21431a6e1726e7f4d8d8c9443.mp4?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dhanra的冲突与角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个短小的冒险将Roshi带入了传说中的战士和保护者的堡垒Dhanra村。村子里居住着五彩斑斓的角色和敌人，每个角色都有独特的美学、机制和个性。这些角色推动着叙述，探讨他们的能力和技术如何引发冲突，审视这些互动中义务、风险、控制和自由的关系。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/29459aaa6c203f666010ec791efa6278.poster.avif?t=1771652205\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/29459aaa6c203f666010ec791efa6278.webm?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/29459aaa6c203f666010ec791efa6278.mp4?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/83e4b94811a14f469cfe7f21703ff974.poster.avif?t=1771652205\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/83e4b94811a14f469cfe7f21703ff974.webm?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136460/extras/83e4b94811a14f469cfe7f21703ff974.mp4?t=1771652205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
